      <description>&lt;p&gt;Next week I&amp;rsquo;m off to Ireland for a few days to attend a wedding. I thought I had a suitable suit to wear but this turned
out not to be the case. I merely had a black pair of shoes. I don&amp;rsquo;t think I even have suitable socks. Unless I try out
the Jacko look and go with white socks and black shoes? Somehow I don&amp;rsquo;t think my girlfriend would be too impressed. So
this weekend I was ordered to buy a suit.&lt;/p&gt;
